&lt;li&gt;Commercial curiosity - you want to understand what drives the numbers, not just produce them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accuracy and ownership - reconciliations tie out and deadlines hold.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
