&lt;p&gt;We are in an exciting phase of growth, expanding rapidly across Europe and internationally, with teams located in Munich, London, Nottingham, Stockholm, and Atlanta.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While we have regional offices, our vision is for our global sales teams to collaborate closely, sharing best practices and continually refining our sales strategy. We are seeking talented and ambitious individuals who want to join our global expansion efforts and support the establishment of our presence in Central and Eastern Europe, based out of our Munich office. Our Munich team will be responsible for the DACH region, Poland, the Czech Republic, and Slovakia.&lt;/p&gt;
