&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in German with intermediate proficiency in English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A passion for sales and phone-based sales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Openness to change and willingness to contribute ideas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Initiative and excellent self-management: You know how to prioritize to make the most of your day.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in the following areas:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;B2B Sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ideally, knowledge of financial products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building and maintaining a customer base and managing it in a CRM system.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
