&lt;p&gt;Risk team is a global team covering Portfolio Analytics, Credit and Commercial Strategy, Underwriting and Collections. We&#39;re on a mission to grow Liberis into the world&#39;s leading embedded business finance provider, and we&#39;re looking for a Senior Credit &amp;amp; Commercial Strategy Analyst to help us make that happen!&lt;/p&gt;
