&lt;p&gt;Liberis is in the middle of a meaningful shift.&amp;nbsp;We started as a single-product business and are quickly becoming a truly multi-product embedded finance company, with different funding structures, revenue models and customer relationships sitting alongside each other in the same portfolio. That complexity creates real demand for better data, better insight and clearer thinking about how all of it fits together - with this role sitting at the centre of that challange!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
