&lt;p&gt;You will own the data and insights product for Liberis, building the foundations that let our commercial, credit and operations teams actually understand the business they&#39;re running. That means, thinking carefully about the entities in our data model, how products and customers relate to each other, how those relationships surface in reporting and analysis - and how it eventually all comes out in great dashboards, tools and self-serve capabilities. This is about shipp

